Yeah, Shredder is trying to get even with Quickstrike.

::Shredder::

Shredder grunts in pain as shots hit him repeatedly, sending him flying into 
a tree, almost smashing through it. He jumps down from the tree, wincing as 
his damaged leg touched the ground.

Shredder looks at KitKat, and with a snarl, opens fire with his remaining 
chain gun. He had lost the other one while being slammed into the tree.
